<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Knowledge Base</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap">
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/a076d05399.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <style>
        /* General Styles */
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        body {
            background-color: #0a0f1c;
            color: #fff;
            display: flex;
        }

        /* Grid Background */
        body::before {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            background: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/grid-me.png') repeat;
            opacity: 0.2;
            z-index: -1;
        }

        /* Sidebar */
        .sidebar {
            width: 250px;
            background: #16243a;
            height: 100vh;
            padding-top: 20px;
            position: fixed;
            transition: 0.3s;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }

        .sidebar.collapsed {
            width: 70px;
        }

        .sidebar h2 {
            color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 20px;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .sidebar.collapsed h2 {
            display: none;
        }

        .sidebar a {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            color: #ddd;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: 0.3s;
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        .sidebar a i {
            margin-right: 10px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        .sidebar.collapsed a span {
            display: none;
        }

        .sidebar a:hover {
            background: #1abc9c;
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Toggle Button */
        .toggle-btn {
            position: absolute;
            top: 15px;
            right: 10px;
            background: #1abc9c;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            cursor: pointer;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        /* Content */
        .content {
            margin-left: 270px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: calc(100% - 270px);
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .sidebar.collapsed + .content {
            margin-left: 90px;
            width: calc(100% - 90px);
        }

        section {
            background: #16243a;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0px 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        h1, h2 {
            color: #fff;
        }

        /* Code Blocks */
        .code-block {
            background: #1e2a3a;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            overflow-x: auto;
            font-size: 14px;
            position: relative;
        }

        .code-block::before {
            content: attr(data-lang);
            position: absolute;
            top: 8px;
            left: 15px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #1abc9c;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .method-get { color: #1abc9c; }
        .method-post { color: #ff7f50; }

        /* Alert Cards */
        .alert {
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 15px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .alert i {
            font-size: 18px;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .alert.note { background: #007bff; }
        .alert.warning { background: #ffcc00; color: #000; }
        .alert.info { background: #1abc9c; }
        
        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .sidebar { width: 200px; }
            .sidebar.collapsed { width: 60px; }
            .content { margin-left: 210px; width: calc(100% - 210px); }
            .sidebar.collapsed + .content { margin-left: 80px; width: calc(100% - 80px); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="sidebar">
        <button class="toggle-btn" onclick="toggleSidebar()">â˜°</button>
        <h2>Knowledge Base</h2>
        <a href="#introduction"><i class="fas fa-home"></i> <span>Introduction</span></a>
        <a href="#get-started"><i class="fas fa-play"></i> <span>Get Started</span></a>
        <a href="#api"><i class="fas fa-code"></i> <span>API Docs</span></a>
        <a href="#user-guide"><i class="fas fa-book"></i> <span>User Guide</span></a>
        <a href="#changelog"><i class="fas fa-history"></i> <span>Changelog</span></a>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <section id="introduction">
            <h1>Enhance <span style="color: #007bff;">Team</span> <span style="color: #1abc9c;">Efficiency</span></h1>
            <p>Welcome to the Knowledge Base. Here, you'll find all the documentation to help you integrate and use our software.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="get-started">
            <h2>Get Started</h2>
            <p>Follow these steps to install:</p>
            <div class="code-block" data-lang="bash">
                <pre>npm install my-app</pre>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="api">
            <h2>API Documentation</h2>
            <div class="code-block method-get" data-lang="GET">
                <pre>GET /api/users
{
    "id": 1,
    "name": "John Doe"
}</pre>
            </div>
            <div class="code-block method-post" data-lang="POST">
                <pre>POST /api/users
{
    "name": "Jane Doe",
    "email": "jane@example.com"
}</pre>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section id="user-guide">
            <h2>User Guide</h2>
            <p>Navigate the dashboard and explore features.</p>
        </section>

        <section id="changelog">
            <h2>Changelog</h2>
            <p>Version 1.0.1 - Bug fixes and improvements.</p>

            <div class="alert note">
                <i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Note: This is an important update.
            </div>

            <div class="alert warning">
                <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i> Warning: Ensure backups before updating.
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <script>
        function toggleSidebar() {
            document.querySelector(".sidebar").classList.toggle("collapsed");
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>
